description:
Are you a prospective college student? Do you have a desire for success? Learn how to avoid the clunky freshman transition and put yourself on a common sense path to success in college. You will learn all about common mistakes college students often make in their classes during their freshman year as well as time management and study techniques that can be applied to all of your classes.

After this course, you should be able to:

1. Be more aware of the difficulty of college class

2. Be able to develop a proper college study plan 

3. Be able to practice you newly learned notetaking and study skills in a demo lecture/exam
title: Simple Techniques to Succeed in College: Learn in 1 day
